**Option 2: Deploy it online (FREE)**

### Deploy on Vercel (Recommended - Super Easy!)
1. Go to https://vercel.com
2. Sign up with GitHub
3. Click **"Add New Project"**
4. Import your `brew-bites-social` repo
5. Click **"Deploy"**
6. Wait 2 minutes → You get a live URL like `brew-bites-social.vercel.app`
7. Share that URL with anyone! 

### Deploy on Netlify (Alternative)
1. Go to https://netlify.com
2. Sign up with GitHub
3. Click **"Add new site"** → **"Import an existing project"**
4. Connect to your GitHub repo
5. Build settings:
   - Build command: `npm run build`
   - Publish directory: `.next`
6. Click **"Deploy"**

